ChangeLog
=========
* Wed Apr 14 2010 mbhangui@gmail.com
Release 1.7.3 Start 31/03/2010

1.  Added new program swaks - Swiss Army Knife for SMTP
2.  Fix extra new lines after Deliverd-To header
3.  fix binding on ipv6 address in timeoutconn.c
4.  Added option to create QMQP service in svctool, RPM
5.  added -fno-strict-aliasing to compilation flags
6.  configure script now detects missing components
7.  preline segfaults [2983128]
8.  use HOSTNAME environment variable to record host in qmail-queue.c (bypass gethostname()
9.  Change permissions of cdb files to indimail in qmailctl
10. Upgrade to clamav-0.96
11. Define environment variable AUTHSERVICE in courier-imap authmodule (authindi) to denote authentication for imap, pop3 or webmail
12. Added ACCT_INACT_EXPIRY, PASSWORD_EXPIRY variables in iauth.so pam plugin to enable pam-checkpwd (pam checkpassword) to return failures on account and password expiry
13. Fixed maths in calculating account/password expiry (iauth.c, pam-multi.c)
14. Added domain limits in iauth.so
15. fixed domain_expiry, passwd_expiry getting reset in vmoddomlimits
16. added domain limits query in inlookup (replaced LPWD_QUERY with LIMIT_QUERY)
17. use inquery in vchkpass, authindi, iauth.so for domain limits (when QUERY_CACHE is defined)
18. Renamed vmoddomlimits to vlimit
